\newlabel{fig:api-coverage}{{5}{24}{API coverage across the benchmark survey. OpenMP (50 benchmarks), MPI (45), and CUDA (38) dominate, with OpenACC (17), HIP (15), and MPI+OpenMP (15) forming a second tier. OpenCL (13) and Kokkos (12) bridge the second and third tiers. OpenMP Target (8), SYCL (7), and RAJA (7) form a third tier}{figure.caption.28}{}}
