\newlabel{fig:selection-funnel}{{13}{32}{HeCBench kernel selection funnel. Starting from 522 kernels spanning CUDA, HIP, SYCL, and OpenMP at commit \texttt {22785cdd}, successive filters for API completeness (329 with all 4~variants), build infrastructure (327), self-checking output patterns (242), and complexity bounds yield a 60-kernel working set. Manual curation further narrows this to 10~evaluation kernels (25~specs; see Section~\ref {sec:benchmark-curation})}{figure.caption.39}{}}
